title: Was Flight MH370 Found with an Eerie Black Box Recording Saying: “SOS, They Are Not Human”?
subtitle: An Internet hoax links missing Malaysian Airlines Flight MH370 with — what else? — aliens.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A black box recording has surfaced featuring an eerie message that suggests the disappearance of Malaysia Flight MH370 involved extraterrestrials.
